{"tid":775083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行雷閃電會出事","createTime":"2018-08-11T00:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T00:35:54.000Z","uid":195944,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"259276a4ef4d7b95c3e27e4473f311cdf2a50e3d","tid":775083,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T00:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知沙中線 膠鐵 防唔防水呢？<br />\n<br />\n話晒都係千年一遇暴乳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7882fe9169e9b2d6e48dc62191fdeb61f2ac088","tid":775083,"uid":195944,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T00:37:59.000Z","msg":"地鐵膠層好似話地下水流失都會令沉降增加<br />\n<br />\n咁個天就幫手補充返啲水<br />\n<br />\n唔知啲樓會唔會升返上黎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望落大啲雨 等啲樓升快啲啦<br />\n<br />\n唔單止樓價要升 實際高度都要升㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家說對不對<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b178e7b9fb547ced7fac4c580cbc13be56261d3","tid":775083,"uid":195944,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T00:41:47.000Z","msg":"仲有條膠鐵<br />\n<br />\n希望佢電制房啲去水系統唔係假啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n等陣短路火燭 開唔到車就唔好啦<br />\n<br />\n仲有幾千萬蝗蟲要搭㗎<br />\n<br />\n開唔到車 每日損失幾千億 邊個賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934c56bf9157a0feb0b23321b209934734061143","tid":775083,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T00:46:45.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母吖<br />\n<br />\n諗住去香港大學站行下 去7仔買domdom<br />\n<br />\n咁室內地方就廢事帶遮<br />\n<br />\n點知成身俾水滴濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原內係地鐵站裡面都要擔遮㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你條鐵漏水嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8382336c24cd298078ae7c442f41622dd2e5844","tid":775083,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好似停咗雨喇"},{"pid":"51252d7c64ef51f130aa39bffd3c23813919f8a8","tid":775083,"uid":101541,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:05:25.000Z","msg":"好味呀"},{"pid":"51c140c7ed9ad13fc2ec8472f97fcf2b653abe1c","tid":775083,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51252d7c64ef51f130aa39bffd3c23813919f8a8","tid":775083,"uid":101541,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:05:25.000Z","msg":"好味呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:11:07.000Z","msg":"好咩味呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524f6ecdc4b43c9fada9d8946b1c3e9a076579c3","tid":775083,"uid":101541,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"51c140c7ed9ad13fc2ec8472f97fcf2b653abe1c","tid":775083,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51252d7c64ef51f130aa39bffd3c23813919f8a8","tid":775083,"uid":101541,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:05:25.000Z","msg":"好味呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:11:07.000Z","msg":"好咩味呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif