s/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9fdd95e252ce4ebd365f300e1e96e1deaa7b1e","tid":775083,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:43:01.000Z","msg":"有無人搭地鐵時 發現周圍都有漏水？<br />\n<br />\n係邊個站？ <br />\n<br />\n我就見過北角 香港大學站漏晒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34ee241e702929cd0d718d1c7cf741f8cf4b334","tid":775083,"uid":195944,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:37:39.000Z","msg":"醜聞纏身的港鐵竟不敵「黃雨」來襲，今日(11日)至少2個港鐵站出現「室內落雨」情況。有網民今早在社交網站上載影片，東鐵<span style=\"color: red;\">太和站</span>一個月台牆身出現嚴重漏水，疑似由天花板漏出，並形成小型瀑布，雨水傾瀉程度與外間的大雨不相上下，令月台地面出現大攤積水。東網今早亦收到讀者報料，西鐵<span style=\"color: red;\">元朗站</span>大堂亦出現大範圍漏水，地面濕漉漉，港鐵出動近20名職員幫忙拖地，場面墟冚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係室內有無擔遮呀？"},{"pid":"34046e080ee5b064609fb71967dc042e920cc3a8","tid":775083,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:44:02.000Z","msg":"人造島又有冇出事 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a48ebf8a1c7c0d6a2761ed95a05c0f3e34da6be","tid":775083,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34046e080ee5b064609fb71967dc042e920cc3a8","tid":775083,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:44:02.000Z","msg":"人造島又有冇出事 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:55:22.000Z","msg":"打風先問蝗造島<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e938cb0c6b5db433ca733800fc66dfaa0cc595","tid":775083,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"